      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NATISA'S SECRET (4) has a strong record this trip with four wins and four placings from 10 starts. Hit the frame latest (22.71) when third at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to be in the finish. HEY BUBBA LOUIE (3) has missed the frame at last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his sharp 18.24 win at Richmond over 320m. Top win three back and can measure up again. NOVA REIGN (1) goes very well at the course and distance with seven wins and a placing from 14 starts. Was out of the placings last time (30.37) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 7 lengths. Can feature in the finish. PROUD CHOICE (2) can sneak into the finish.",
